OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCo Down family on course to
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffinish 50th marathon       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A County Down family, who campaigned   
OL,6, for assisted wheelchairs to be allowed 
OL,7, in the London Marathon, will soon      
OL,8, complete their 50th marathon.          
OL,10,FBefore 2022, assisted wheelchairs were 
OL,11,Fnot allowed on the course.             
OL,13,FBut David and Sandra Kerr campaigned   
OL,14,Ffor seven years, so they could take    
OL,15,Fpart in the race with their son Aaron  
OL,16,Fwho has a series of complex needs.     
OL,18,FSpeaking at the halfway mark in the    
OL,19,Frace on Sunday, David said it was      
OL,20,F"phenomenal" to be there.              
